CMP.education+='<h3>Trade-offs</h3><div class="table-wrap"><table><tr><th>✅ Pros</th><th>❌ Cons</th></tr><tr><td style="color:var(--green)">FREE school fees (saves $11k+/yr)</td><td>75–90 min commute each way to Sydney CBD</td></tr><tr><td style="color:var(--green)">Rent $550–$750/wk (vs $850+ in Sydney metro)</td><td>Fewer kids activity options locally (ice rinks, circus)</td></tr><tr><td style="color:var(--green)">Beautiful beaches — Terrigal, Avoca</td><td>Need a car — less public transport than Sydney</td></tr><tr><td style="color:var(--green)">Strong community feel — less hectic than Sydney</td><td>Further from Sydney airport for UK flights</td></tr><tr><td style="color:var(--green)">More space — bigger houses, gardens</td><td>Frankie may have fewer job options locally</td></tr></table></div>';

