CMP.costs+='<h3>Why is it free?</h3><ul class="ts" style="margin:8px 0 0 20px;line-height:2"><li><strong>Victoria:</strong> Treats 482 visa holders similarly to permanent residents for education. All areas eligible — no restrictions.</li><li><strong>NSW Regional:</strong> From Term 1 2025, NSW waives fees for 482 visa holders living <strong>outside Greater Sydney and Wollongong</strong>. Part of a push to support regional families filling skills shortages.</li><li><strong>NSW Metro:</strong> Full fees apply. No waiver for Sydney, Wollongong, or surrounding metro areas.</li></ul>';

